es for customers who contracted before February 1, 2019 to receive electric supply from a third party provider registered with Appalachian Power Company Virginia. If you have questions,  ...    Tariff 3 Tariff 3-This document contains rates and charges for non-residential customers who contracted after February 1, 2019 to receive electric supply from a supplier registered with Appalachian Power Company Virginia. If you have questions,  ...    - Select Residential & Non-Residential Customer Charges\n\n### Welcome back! Please login to manage your account.\n\n"
